name: lexicographicallyPrecedes(_:by:)
desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether the sequence precedes another sequence in a lexicographical (dictionary) ordering, using the given predicate to compare elements.
declaration: func lexicographicallyPrecedes<OtherSequence>(_ other: OtherSequence, by areInIncreasingOrder: (IndexingIterator<Array<UInt8>>.Element, IndexingIterator<Array<UInt8>>.Element) throws -> Bool) rethrows -> Bool where OtherSequence : Sequence, IndexingIterator<Array<UInt8>>.Element == OtherSequence.Element
